block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Learn how to fold this Flying Witch designed by Kunihiko Kasahara. You could also use it as an origami wizard. It is the perfect origami decoration for Halloween. Try it out, I hope you like it. Learn it in less than a minute! Enjoy!!! Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
